{"tid":2437500,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽教既蒸水蛋","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T14:51:30.000Z","uid":276969,"like":16,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d38bd09e4337c2dac5c6088e4ca9509455cdb629","tid":2437500,"uid":276969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:08:51.000Z","msg":"蒸水蛋係屋企飯桌出現頻率非常高的一味餸。因為食材簡單，做法也簡單，而且滑嘟嘟的口感超級無敵好下飯！我3歲細仔每次看到蒸水蛋都話係啫喱而且搶住大口大口咁食。<br />\n記憶中, 媽媽每次做的蒸水蛋都是零毛孔很水嫩的，所以我總以為這是零難度零失敗的一道菜。然而我自己剛開始學做蒸水蛋的時候, 總係將水蛋蒸成月球表面那般，口感和賣相都相當唔好。於是向媽討教做法後，我每次都輕鬆做出細緻順滑的水蛋。<br />\n食譜和做法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058iq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=93ef584c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNAC7Rt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNAC7Rt.jpg&h=b1537e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10063d94db67a7c7abd62e4ad98b927028788594","tid":2437500,"uid":168703,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d38bd09e4337c2dac5c6088e4ca9509455cdb629","tid":2437500,"uid":276969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:08:51.000Z","msg":"蒸水蛋係屋企飯桌出現頻率非常高的一味餸。因為食材簡單，做法也簡單，而且滑嘟嘟的口感超級無敵好下飯！我3歲細仔每次看到蒸水蛋都話係啫喱而且搶住大口大口咁食。<br />\n記憶中, 媽媽每次做的蒸水蛋都是零毛孔很水嫩的，所以我總以為這是零難度零失敗的一道菜。然而我自己剛開始學做蒸水蛋的時候, 總係將水蛋蒸成月球表面那般，口感和賣相都相當唔好。於是向媽討教做法後，我每次都輕鬆做出細緻順滑的水蛋。<br />\n食譜和做法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058iq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=93ef584c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNAC7Rt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNAC7Rt.jpg&h=b